[
  {
    "id": "ev_first_contact",
    "title": "The Stranded Survey Team",
    "entryNode": "n_intro",
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "n_intro",
        "text": "A rival bloc's survey team is stranded at the relay, their return address burned out. Their leader lowers her weapon first.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_help",
            "text": "Offer them passage through our gate.",
            "effects": [
              { "type": "resource", "resource": "materials", "delta": -5 },
              { "type": "variable", "variable": "trust_rival", "delta": 2 },
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "helped_rivals", "value": true },
              { "type": "queueEvent", "event": "ev_first_contact", "delayDays": 30 }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_help" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_interrogate",
            "text": "[Diplomat] Trade passage for what they know.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "squadHasArchetype", "tag": "diplomat" }],
            "effects": [{ "type": "resource", "resource": "intel", "delta": 8 }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_help" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_data",
            "text": "[Science 5+] Decode their burned-out address instead.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "science", "min": 5 }],
            "effects": [{ "type": "resource", "resource": "exotics", "delta": 2 }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_help" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_leave",
            "text": "Leave them. Not our problem.",
            "effects": [
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "abandoned_rivals", "value": true },
              { "type": "variable", "variable": "trust_rival", "delta": -3 },
              { "type": "fatigue", "scope": "squad", "delta": 5 }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_cold" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_help",
        "text": "The crossing is tense but quiet. Their leader memorizes every face on your team before stepping through.",
        "options": [
          { "id": "o_return", "text": "Return home.", "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_contact" } }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "outcomes": [
      {
        "id": "out_contact",
        "label": "Contact established",
        "effects": [
          { "type": "xp", "scope": "squad", "amount": 10 },
          { "type": "log", "text": "Someone on the other side owes us. Or knows us." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "out_cold",
        "label": "Walked away",
        "effects": [{ "type": "xp", "scope": "squad", "amount": 5 }]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "ev_vy_pilgrim_roads",
    "title": "Pilgrim Roads",
    "entryNode": "n_vy1_arrive",
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_arrive",
        "text": "The gate opens on a terraced holy city, white stone and bell-towers under two suns. The Second Expedition's last transmission is nine days stale. Pilgrim chatter in the market says heretics await 'the Penitence's mercy' — whatever that means, it isn't good.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_move_in",
            "text": "Move in.",
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_gather" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_gather",
        "text": "A day to work before the plan has to be a plan. Time enough to learn something, if you're careful about who's listening.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_pilgrims",
            "text": "Listen among the pilgrims.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "not", "condition": { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_pilgrims", "value": true } },
              { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "diplomacy", "min": 4 }
            ],
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_pilgrims", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_pilgrims_detail" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_patrols",
            "text": "Shadow the temple patrols.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "not", "condition": { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_patrols", "value": true } },
              { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "combat", "min": 5 }
            ],
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_patrols", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_patrols_detail" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_relay",
            "text": "Okafor: tap the temple relay traffic.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "not", "condition": { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_comms", "value": true } },
              { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "science", "min": 6 }
            ],
            "effects": [
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_comms", "value": true },
              { "type": "variable", "variable": "doubt", "delta": 1 }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_relay_detail" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_move_on",
            "text": "We've learned enough. Move to the plan.",
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_plan" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_pilgrims_detail",
        "text": "Words drift between processions: 'Oru walks where he is worshipped.' Doctrine, not proof — but it's the first crack in how they explain him.",
        "options": [
          { "id": "o_vy1_pilgrims_continue", "text": "Continue.", "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_gather" } }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_patrols_detail",
        "text": "Guard rotations are looser than they look — predictable, if you watch long enough.",
        "options": [
          { "id": "o_vy1_patrols_continue", "text": "Continue.", "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_gather" } }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_relay_detail",
        "speaker": "Dr. A. Okafor",
        "text": "Okafor taps the relay traffic and goes quiet for a long moment. 'That's encrypted,' she finally says. 'Gods don't need encryption.'",
        "options": [
          { "id": "o_vy1_relay_continue", "text": "Continue.", "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_gather" } }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_plan",
        "text": "Three ways in, and none of them easy.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_uniform_choice",
            "text": "Guard uniforms — walk in as temple staff.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_approach_uniform", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_uniform" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_worker_choice",
            "text": "Provision workers — go in with the grain carts.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "not", "condition": { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_dessik_refused", "value": true } }
            ],
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_approach_worker", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_dessik" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_assault_choice",
            "text": "Open assault — go in loud.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_approach_assault", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy1_assault" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_uniform",
        "text": "The barracks courtyard empties out before shift change.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_knockout",
            "text": "Knock out a lone guard and take his colors.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "combat", "min": 5 }],
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_uniform_knockout", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_uniform_body" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_bathhouse",
            "text": "Find another way: lift a set from the bath-house during vigil hour.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_uniform_stolen", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy1_uniform" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_uniform_body",
        "text": "He's out cold and will stay that way a while. What now?",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_hide_body",
            "text": "Hide him in the cistern.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_body_hidden", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy1_uniform" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_leave_body",
            "text": "Leave him. Move fast.",
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy1_uniform" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy1_dessik",
        "text": "Broker Dessik will get you work passes — for a price. His son Ilo is condemned as a smuggler, held somewhere in the Penitence. 'Bring him out,' Dessik says, 'and the carts are yours.'",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_dessik_accept",
            "text": "Swear it.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_owe_ilo", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy1_worker" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy1_dessik_refuse",
            "text": "Refuse. Find another way in.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_dessik_refused", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy1_plan" }
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "outcomes": [
      {
        "id": "out_vy1_uniform",
        "label": "Infiltration prepared — guard colors",
        "effects": [{ "type": "unlockMission", "mission": "m_vy_2" }]
      },
      {
        "id": "out_vy1_worker",
        "label": "Infiltration prepared — provision carts",
        "effects": [{ "type": "unlockMission", "mission": "m_vy_2" }]
      },
      {
        "id": "out_vy1_assault",
        "label": "Plan: open assault",
        "effects": [{ "type": "unlockMission", "mission": "m_vy_2" }]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "ev_vy_penitence",
    "title": "The Penitence",
    "entryNode": "n_vy2_router",
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_router",
        "text": "The plan carries you to the temple gate. Whatever happens next, it happens fast.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_route_uniform",
            "text": "Approach in guard colors.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_approach_uniform", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_gate" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_route_worker",
            "text": "Approach with the grain carts.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_approach_worker", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_b_kitchens" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_route_assault",
            "text": "Hit the gate head-on.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_approach_assault", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_c_assault_1" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_a_gate",
        "text": "Guard colors, temple gate, morning shift change.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_case_complication",
            "text": "Move for the checkpoint.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_uniform_knockout", "value": true },
              { "type": "not", "condition": { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_body_hidden", "value": true } }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_complication" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_case_smooth",
            "text": "Move for the checkpoint.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_uniform_knockout", "value": true },
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_body_hidden", "value": true }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_case_seal",
            "text": "Move for the checkpoint.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_uniform_stolen", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_seal" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_a_complication",
        "text": "A sergeant squints at your face. He swears he's seen the missing guard's watch on your wrist.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_talk",
            "text": "Talk him down.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "diplomacy", "min": 5 }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_overpower",
            "text": "Take the checkpoint quietly.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "combat", "min": 6 }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_push",
            "text": "Push past before he thinks it through.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_alarm", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_a_seal",
        "text": "The inner gate wants a rank-seal your borrowed colors don't have.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_bluff_easy",
            "text": "Bluff as new transfers.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_pilgrims", "value": true },
              { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "diplomacy", "min": 4 }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_bluff_hard",
            "text": "Bluff as new transfers.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_pilgrims", "value": false },
              { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "diplomacy", "min": 5 }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_ossuary",
            "text": "Slip through the ossuary passage instead.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_patrols", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_push2",
            "text": "Push past before they think it through.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_alarm", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_a_cells" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_a_cells",
        "text": "Cell block. Rows of them, and behind one door, the Second Expedition.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_quiet",
            "text": "Quiet route out. Slow, but quiet.",
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_bottleneck_ab" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_a_bell",
            "text": "Bell-tower diversion. Fast, but loud.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_alarm", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_bottleneck_ab" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_b_kitchens",
        "text": "Grain carts, meal rounds — the prison runs on ritual, predictable as a clock. You find the cell block. And you find Ilo, Dessik's son, three doors down from the expedition.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_b_free_ilo",
            "text": "Free Ilo too. A promise is a promise.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_ilo_freed", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_b_exfil" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_b_leave_ilo",
            "text": "Leave him. The expedition comes first.",
            "effects": [
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_ilo_abandoned", "value": true },
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_alarm", "value": true },
              { "type": "injury", "scope": "randomSquadMember", "injury": "inj_shaken" }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_bottleneck_ab" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_b_exfil",
        "text": "Two extra bodies to move quietly, and the corridor guard rotation won't wait.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_b_resolve",
            "text": "Hold the nerve, hold the pace.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "resolve", "min": 5 }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_bottleneck_ab" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_b_alarm",
            "text": "Force it and take the noise.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_alarm", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_bottleneck_ab" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_c_assault_1",
        "text": "The wall guns track before you're in range. Precursor-tech, someone says — the light doesn't look like any weapon you've drilled against.",
        "options": [
          { "id": "o_vy2_c_1", "text": "Keep moving.", "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_c_assault_2" } }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_c_assault_2",
        "text": "Small arms fire washes off a shield you can't see the edge of. This was never going to be a fair fight.",
        "options": [
          { "id": "o_vy2_c_2", "text": "Keep moving.", "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_c_assault_3" } }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_c_assault_3",
        "text": "No path through. Just a choice about how this ends.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_c_press",
            "text": "Press the breach.",
            "effects": [
              { "type": "injury", "scope": "randomSquadMember", "injury": "inj_wounded" },
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_captured", "value": true }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_bottleneck_c" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_c_fallback",
            "text": "Fall back to the gate.",
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_captured", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy2_bottleneck_c" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_bottleneck_ab",
        "text": "The First Blade already knows you're here.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_bn_alarm",
            "text": "Bells overhead — they moved fast to get ahead of you.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_alarm", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy2_next" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy2_bn_quiet",
            "text": "No bells. Just a silence that means they already knew.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_alarm", "value": false }],
            "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy2_next" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy2_bottleneck_c",
        "text": "Gear confiscated, cells beside the very people you came for — the rescue, inverted. At dawn, the cell doors open on their own. The yard awaits.",
        "options": [
          { "id": "o_vy2_c_move", "text": "Move.", "next": { "kind": "end", "outcome": "out_vy2_next" } }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "outcomes": [
      {
        "id": "out_vy2_next",
        "label": "The First Blade closes in",
        "effects": [{ "type": "unlockMission", "mission": "m_vy_3" }]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "ev_vy_first_blade",
    "title": "The First Blade",
    "entryNode": "n_vy3_intro",
    "nodes": [
      {
        "id": "n_vy3_intro",
        "text": "The gate's other side. Whatever plan carried you this far, it ends here.",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy3_intro_ab",
            "text": "Seryn Vael and his honor guard corner you in the processional court, mid-escape.",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_captured", "value": false }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy3_confront" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy3_intro_c",
            "text": "Execution yard, dawn. Seryn reads the sentence: 'All of you burn at dusk. Oru is merciful — dusk is hours away.'",
            "requirements": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_captured", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy3_confront" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "n_vy3_confront",
        "speaker": "Seryn Vael",
        "text": "Seryn draws level, blade still sheathed. 'Say what you came to say — or don't.'",
        "options": [
          {
            "id": "o_vy3_convince_b1_win",
            "text": "Convince him — a god who feeds on executions deserves no First Blade.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "variable", "variable": "doubt", "op": "<", "value": 1 },
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_pilgrims", "value": false },
              { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "diplomacy", "min": 7 }
            ],
            "effects": [{ "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_first_convinced", "value": true }],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy3_resolve_intro" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy3_convince_b1_fail",
            "text": "Convince him — a god who feeds on executions deserves no First Blade.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "variable", "variable": "doubt", "op": "<", "value": 1 },
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_pilgrims", "value": false },
              {
                "type": "not",
                "condition": { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "diplomacy", "min": 7 }
              }
            ],
            "next": { "kind": "node", "node": "n_vy3_hardens" }
          },
          {
            "id": "o_vy3_convince_b2_win",
            "text": "Convince him — quote his own scripture back: a god who feeds on executions deserves no First Blade.",
            "requirements": [
              { "type": "variable", "variable": "doubt", "op": "<", "value": 1 },
              { "type": "flag", "flag": "f_vy_intel_pilgrims", "value": true },
              { "type": "squadSkillAtLeast", "skill": "diplomacy", "min": 6 }
            ],
